tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE thumbnails (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    image_url VARCHAR(255),
    alt_text VARCHAR(255),
    variant_name VARCHAR(50),
    click_through_rate FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE ab_test_results (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    test_id UUID,
    variant_id UUID,
    click_through_rate FLOAT,
    conversion_rate FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE Clicks (
    click_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    video_id INT,
    experiment_id INT,
    group_id INT,
    click_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    PRIMARY KEY (click_id, user_id, video_id, experiment_id, group_id)
);
